title: 12 dead in military plane crash in Afghanistan
text:
AFGHANISTAN (NEWS 1130) â€“ Twelve people have been killed in a US military plane crash in Afghanistan.
Five of the dead are the service member crew when the C-130 transport plane went down at Jalalabad Airport.
Two civilians on the ground were also killed.
No reason for the crash has been given.
